@startuml
title Completion Notification Saga - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

participant "visits-service" as Visits
database "visits.NotificationSaga" as SagaDB
queue "RabbitMQ\npetclinic.events" as MQ
participant "mailer-service (Go)" as Mailer
participant "SMTP" as SMTP
participant "staff dashboard" as Staff

Visits -> SagaDB: create saga row PENDING\ncorrelation=eventId
Visits -> MQ: publish VisitCompletedEvent
MQ -> Mailer: deliver event
Mailer -> SMTP: send visit summary email
alt email accepted
  Mailer -> MQ: publish NotificationAck(originalEventId)
  MQ -> Visits: consume ack
  Visits -> SagaDB: mark COMPLETED
else delivery failed
  Mailer -> MQ: publish NotificationFailed(originalEventId, reason)
  MQ -> Visits: consume failure
  Visits -> SagaDB: mark COMPENSATED
  Visits -> MQ: publish VisitManualFollowUpRequiredEvent
  MQ -> Staff: show manual follow-up task
end

note over Visits,SagaDB
Publisher + DB commit is not atomic in v1.
Production-grade design should add a transactional outbox.
end note
@enduml
